songs.title: Galata Qabanneerra
songs.lyrics:
Galata Qabanneerra si Waaqessuuf dhufnee jirraa
Ulfina Qabanneerraa si waaqessuuf dhufnee jirra
Galata qabna waaqayyoof galata qabna *4

Iyyaarikoon jigee dura keenyatti
Gimbichi cabe dabarree nuti
Waan jennu hin dhabnu galata qabna
Gooftaa guddaa kana ililleen ol qabna

Ilillee qabna Waaqayyoof ilillee qabna *4

Galataan baanee galatan galle
Gooftaa qabanne nuti hin saalfanne
Harka abbummaasaan nuun dura darbee 
Nu gammachiise galaanan hire

Galata qabna waaqayyoof galata qabna *4

Hoo Hoo Galata Jenna *6
Gaarri guddaan  jigee(*2)
Kan nuun duraa jigee(*2)
In caccabee Jigee(*2)
Kunoo har'a

Hoo Hooo Galata Jenna *8

songs.title: Ati waaquma
songs.lyrics:
Lubbuun kan jiran uumama keessaa
Maal akkam godheen itti an si fakkeessa
Ulfina guddaan surraan kan iftu
Qofaa kee mootii qofaa kee bittu*2
Waaqa akkasii kan an waaqessu
Ulee aboonsaa hunda gaggeessu*2
Ya Waaq ati Waaquma
YESUUS ati Waaquma
Kan akka keetii eessatti argama(*3)*2
Gurguddoonni beektonni sin qixxaatani
Hidhaa namaa hiikuu hin danda’ani
Eeyyee hin danda’ani, dhugaadha hin danda’ani
Maqaan kee haa mo’u waaqaaf lafa irratti
Nuti si waaqessina hamma jiraannutti
Hamma jiraannutti mo’i atumti*2

Jaalalaan loltee kan nu mo’atte
Araara guddaan kan nu harkifte
Ijoollee ko jechuu nuttin qaanofne
Akka hojii keenyaaf nun balleessine
Toloota gootee kan nu lakkoofte
Gochaan kee heddu nu boqochiifte*2
Ya Waaq…

songs.title: Sin Mararfadhaa
songs.lyrics:
Sin Mararfadhaa an sin Jaalladhaa
Maqaa ke yesuus ittiinan dhaadadha
